 year old punk-rocker and a 15 year old runaway girl.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.3618,"vote_count":21,"poster_path":"/zcMfPbVEm58E9CCUbabYEwlHGC6.jpg","release_date":"2001-10-25","vote_average":6.19,"backdrop_path":"/3AizwQluvjzFRP5o8MYvHxh14A9.jpg","original_title":"Engel & Joe","original_language":"de"},{"id":11313,"adult":false,"title":"Hearts in Atlantis","video":false,"overview":"A widowed mother and her son change when a mysterious stranger enters their lives.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.3377,"vote_count":602,"poster_path":"/qPTEh8vutS5FSCDoR16MWVGHqTm.jpg","release_date":"2001-09-28","vote_average":6.758,"backdrop_path":"/zi8XZEYs7R7bQLmEffs7V46k2ZA.jpg","original_title":"Hearts in Atlantis","original_language":"en"},{"id":864069,"adult":false,"title":"Kyōkai-sen no mukō-gawa","video":false,"overview":"One day, Hiroshi was helping in an acquaintance's shop and accidentally breaks a jar that cost 1 million yen. Hiroshi can't pay for that and he calls his parents' house as a last resort. He receives news that his father is ill with only 1 year left. Hiroshi wants to make his father happy and decides on a fake marriage. They find a lesbian teacher called Ayako interested in fake marriage on the internet. However, when they go to meet her the angry girlfriend of Ayako called Ami shows up and a man tries to catch Hiroshi for not paying his 1 million yen debt. They steal a van and Ami, Hiroshi and Toshiya drive off in hopes of finding Ayako.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.1833,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/bQk5WviC8waRhF11ctGGrhzCrfS.jpg","release_date":"1998-10-31","vote_average":2,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"境界線の向こう側","original_language":"ja"},{"id":864084,"adult":false,"title":"Ritual to Call Summer","video":false,"overview":"Yuta is attacked by a pair of masked men and tries to escape. He is cornered in a factory by two men and left bleeding. Yuta decides to take revenge on the spot, but one of the masked men, Kurumada, begins to feel in love with Yuta. After that, incidents continued to occur at the same factory. Yuta, who is wandering around looking for a masked man, gives his body to Henmi, a gay man, on the condition that he cooperate with the search. Yuta finds the factory where he was raped, but is confronted by a masked man, Kurumada, who confesses his love for him.","genre_ids":[18,9648],"popularity":0.2068,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/hG81x9HKqr5tOzpKkRTTIlrYbNz.jpg","release_date":"1995-07-31","vote_average":4,"backdrop_path":"/14Zu6iSW4YdAAMsK84yJlLQUQuw.jpg","original_title":"夏を呼ぶ儀式","original_language":"ja"},{"id":472649,"adult":false,"title":"Sarah Plays a Werewolf","video":false,"overview":"17-year old Sarah, filled with adolescent angst, is an extreme person who in her rehearsals with a theatre group is transformed until she is almost in a trance, and her performances at home or elsewhere verge on excess. A cold, intellectual father, a timid mother, a younger sister and an older brother who has left home complete the picture: a silent time bomb.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2479,"vote_count":19,"poster_path":"/5iKWAcJz709psNINu0GVXdVD8lX.jpg","release_date":"2017-10-03","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/qp8ZhVUVyUTMvL6cGm3vMQ0XCTt.jpg","original_title":"Sarah joue un loup-garou","original_language":"fr"},{"id":11344,"adult":false,"title":"A Bittersweet Life","video":false,"overview":"Kim Sun-woo is an enforcer and manager for a hotel owned by a cold, calculative crime boss, Kang who assigns Sun-woo to a simple errand while he is away on a business trip; to shadow his young mistress, Hee-soo, for fear that she may be cheating on him with a younger man with the mandate that he must kill them both if he discovers their affair.","genre_ids":[28,18,80],"popularity":3.2463,"vote_count":969,"poster_path":"/iqUGAIQqHMMscatykpR6hVBxezA.jpg","release_date":"2005-04-01","vote_average":7.434,"backdrop_path":"/t8EDE4bkYZBaSCo7Gq8uIWtW4pV.jpg","original_title":"달콤한 인생","original_language":"ko"},{"id":11148,"adult":false,"title":"XXY","video":false,"overview":"Alex, an intersexed 15-year-old, is living as a girl, but she and her family begin to wonder whether she's emotionally a boy when another teenager's sexual advances bring the issue to a head. As Alex faces a final decision regarding her gender, she meets both hostility and compassion.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.1596,"vote_count":315,"poster_path":"/4sgoignnXhqjxepHBi2inLFLhSz.jpg","release_date":"2007-06-14","vote_average":6.854,"backdrop_path":"/w1USmlLq33AkiAEIry7k0Hy5GsE.jpg","original_title":"XXY","original_language":"es"},{"id":11151,"adult":false,"title":"Maroa","video":false,"overview":"Eleven-year-old petty criminal Maroa lives with her violent grandmother Brigida in Caracas. After her boyfriend Carlos is involved in a shooting, Maroa is arrested and sent to a school where Joaquin conducts the youth orchestra, and he asks the naturally talented Maroa to join. Days now revolve around the classes that Joaquin, the shy and unconventional teacher, gives her. He is immediately interested in this talented young girl, who lacks all notion of discipline. Joaquin, the only person to offer hope in the midst of her rejection, finds that through Maroa, his world has also changed forever.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2727,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/yM9ACFvYTdc9bGoCpRfGhlhZoT4.jpg","release_date":"2005-09-26","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/wA0TlvRkpp2bDM0lvtGkXpJbFh8.jpg","original_title":"Maroa","original_language":"en"},{"id":11156,"adult":false,"title":"Coco Before Chanel","video":false,"overview":"Several years after leaving the orphanage, to which her father never returned for her, Gabrielle Chanel finds herself working in a provincial bar. She's both a seamstress for the performers and a singer, earning the nickname Coco from the song she sings nightly with her sister. A liaison with Baron Balsan gives her an entree into French society and a chance to develop her gift for designing.","genre_ids":[18,36],"popularity":1.296,"vote_count":1012,"poster_path":"/nNpP1P2EufA6TN7fQOBeHUIVmeH.jpg","release_date":"2009-04-22","vote_average":6.867,"backdrop_path":"/kZkk6iLvFPOiF6Xze2fYSiTbJ1Q.jpg","original_title":"Coco avant Chanel","original_language":"fr"},{"id":11166,"adult":false,"title":"Mother's Elling","video":false,"overview":"Elling has lived with his mother all his life. Mom is the practical one, while Elling ponders the more theoretical aspects of life. He spends his time in their apartment reading books and looking at the neighbours through the living room window. Elling doesn't seem to need to be around others like most people. That's why Elling is less than enthusiastic when his mother suddenly decides to take her son on a beach vacation to Spain. Reluctantly, Elling agrees.  After all, a lady at her age needs a good man by her side. But what Elling refuses to realize is that Mom is not only old, but also sick. Very sick. On her last vacation she tries to get Elling to see that life is bigger than their living room.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":1.1276,"vote_count":35,"poster_path":"/c4eHE3cy5JBjoGSobHxaUkOmv4a.jpg","release_date":"2003-10-10","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/vZ1sMt6bn0pj3aXsJj7ZsmWV5jZ.jpg","original_title":"Mors Elling","original_language":"no"},{"id":11167,"adult":false,"title":"Peeping Tom","video":false,"overview":"Loner Mark Lewis works at a film studio during the day and, at night, takes racy photographs of women. Also he's making a documentary on fear, which involves recording the reactions of victims as he murders them. He befriends Helen, the daughter of the family living in the apartment below his, and he tells her vaguely about the movie he is making.","genre_ids":[27,53,18],"popularity":1.8422,"vote_count":883,"poster_path":"/kM4AfLIlbcuRZ621vYjyeBFkuba.jpg","release_date":"1960-04-07","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/rLm66DbLwxHeRB34oJ1mhsu0urc.jpg","original_title":"Peeping Tom","original_language":"en"},{"id":279722,"adult":false,"title":"Parallel Lives","video":false,"overview":"A college reunion turns into a tangled web of passion, romance and intrigue as old friends and enemies catch up with each other's lives. Includes a long list of stars.","genre_ids":[10770,18],"popularity":0.4642,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/iWYaPaS3DDWQAlzSfbr8xlVcTp5.jpg","release_date":"1994-08-04","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Parallel Lives","original_language":"en"},{"id":1461947,"adult":false,"title":"Real, True 100 Percent Love","video":false,"overview":"After her boyfriend mysteriously vanishes, Elli DeCosta’s personal heartbreak escalates into an international adventure involving Russian agents, the CIA, and a journey to rediscover her voice when he suddenly resurfaces months later.","genre_ids":[10749,10402,35,53],"popularity":0.1643,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Real, True 100 Percent Love","original_language":"en"},{"id":11399,"adult":false,"title":"Look at Me","video":false,"overview":"Talented 20-year-old Lolita dreams of a singing career. But her self-esteem is low due to her weight problem and her narcissistic father, Étienne, a literary star with scant interest in his daughter's life. Lolita finds little comfort in the attentions of her vocal coach, suspecting the woman is using her to meet her influential father. Étienne's second wife proves to be Lolita's only trustworthy ally in her private battle to find a sense of worth.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":0.8195,"vote_count":101,"poster_path":"/kRtLMLdf6PkOjWCvhTpa811aMZy.jpg","release_date":"2004-11-18","vote_average":6.337,"backdrop_path":"/jf2FtZmfwURp9IfD6p7zAtCJkUs.jpg","original_title":"Comme une image","original_language":"fr"},{"id":472713,"adult":false,"title":"Till Human Voices Wake Us","video":false,"overview":"Inspired by the Celtic myths of the Selkies - seals in water and enchanting maidens on land - who storm Manhattan when one of their kind falls for a man drowning under the Brooklyn Bridge.","genre_ids":[878,12,14,10749],"popularity":0.1711,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/rnr18huuwelGODZY2gm7IVs1ibZ.jpg","release_date":"2015-07-25","vote_average":1.5,"backdrop_path":"/zVo8KR9CylYIKxYdqYyQUlqkQtU.jpg","original_title":"Till Human Voices Wake Us","original_language":"en"},{"id":11368,"adult":false,"title":"Blood Simple","video":false,"overview":"The owner of a seedy small-town Texas bar discovers that one of his employees is having an affair with his wife. A chaotic chain of misunderstandings, lies and mischief ensues after he devises a plot to have them murdered.","genre_ids":[80,18,53],"popularity":2.6881,"vote_count":1582,"poster_path":"/svU6pu4lfHn0T5BVZchVxL58HB5.jpg","release_date":"1985-01-18","vote_average":7.252,"backdrop_path":"/rGPoNNk4fvgG2mvkNAxJJPlszOu.jpg","original_title":"Blood Simple","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt0949489","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q5226961","instagram_id":null,"metacritic_id":"movie/lostinbeijing","mydramalist_id":"119928","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/1192806-lost_in_beijing"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":104317,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"DE","release_dates":[{"note":"Berlin International Film Festival ","type":1,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2007-02-16T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","release_dates":[{"note":"Hong Kong Asian Film Festival","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2007-09-26T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2012-09-05T00:00:00.000Z","certific